  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators objective is to assess quality of life and functional outcome in patients
      requiring short-term mechanical ventilation. Additionally, the investigators plan to measure
      the recovery of peripheral muscle strength and respiratory muscle strength during recovery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
